    "description": "Featuring a Sims-inspired building system, randomized cats to take care of, an in-game camera &amp; Instacat feature, and lots of yummy treats to cook &amp; serve to your customers. Your duty as manager of the cat café is to find new forever-homes for the stray cats you take in. But you don't have to let all of your cats go; if you bond with some of them you can choose to let them stay at the café forever!<br><br><br>The game is currently on hold due to the developer being busy with a full-time education.<br><br><strong>More GIFS and images coming soon!</strong><br><br><strong>Build your café!</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1707140/extras/c10cd61da2f8c8ea183e4da539ec98f7.poster.avif?t=1725970729\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1707140/extras/c10cd61da2f8c8ea183e4da539ec98f7.webm?t=1725970729\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1707140/extras/c10cd61da2f8c8ea183e4da539ec98f7.mp4?t=1725970729\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Populate your café with unique cats!</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1707140/extras/ee99d6b8ad06cf090d91c5fbde762a39.poster.avif?t=1725970729\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1707140/extras/ee99d6b8ad06cf090d91c5fbde762a39.webm?t=1725970729\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1707140/extras/ee99d6b8ad06cf090d91c5fbde762a39.mp4?t=1725970729\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Take photos of your cats with the in-game camera!</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1707140/extras/2974d7584720257e612431202b632a15.poster.avif?t=1725970729\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1707140/extras/2974d7584720257e612431202b632a15.webm?t=1725970729\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1707140/extras/2974d7584720257e612431202b632a15.mp4?t=1725970729\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
